{"type":"getPostById","data":{"title":"[tutorial] 讓在 VScode 開發 Java 跟 Intellij 一樣好用的 Extension","date":"2026-03-17T16:00:00.000Z","description":"<h1>📌 簡介</h1>\n<p>讓在 VScode 開發 Java 跟 Intellij 一樣好用 ~~</p>","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"java","_id":"cmnrj7yel004it8zf4wioajmf"}],"content":"\n    <style>\n    .post-lang-switch{\n      position: absolute;\n      top: .75rem;\n      right: .75rem;\n      z-index: 2;\n      color: var(--link, #3273dc);\n    }\n    .post-lang-switch:hover{opacity:.8}\n    </style>\n  \n    <a class=\"post-lang-switch\" href=\"/blog/tutorial-vscode-java-intellij-extension.en/\" title=\"View English version\" aria-label=\"View English version\">\n      <i class=\"fas fa-language\"></i>\n    </a>\n  <h1>📌 簡介</h1>\n<p>讓在 VScode 開發 Java 跟 Intellij 一樣好用 ~~</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h1>🚀 介紹 Extension</h1>\n<h2 id=\"Indention-Setup\">Indention Setup</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://hackmd.io/_uploads/r1akTW6t-e.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://hackmd.io/_uploads/ByA53ZatWg.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"Project-Manager-for-Java\">Project Manager for Java</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://hackmd.io/_uploads/HJ7xkCvqWe.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://hackmd.io/_uploads/HkPqktUtZe.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"Java-Formatter\">Java Formatter</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://hackmd.io/_uploads/rJe0oOnPtZg.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://hackmd.io/_uploads/HkmxF3DtWg.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">&quot;java.format.settings.url&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/google/styleguide/gh-pages/eclipse-java-google-style.xml&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">&quot;java.format.settings.profile&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;GoogleStyle&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"IntelliJ-IDEA-Keybindings\">IntelliJ IDEA Keybindings</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://hackmd.io/_uploads/HkX6tO8F-x.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=k--kato.intellij-idea-keybindings\">https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=k--kato.intellij-idea-keybindings</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"After\">After</h3>\n<h4 id=\"建立新的-Method\">建立新的 Method</h4>\n<ol>\n<li><kbd>Option</kbd> + <kbd>Enter</kbd></li>\n<li>選 <code>Create method xxx</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://hackmd.io/_uploads/HJrUid8YZe.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"Javadoc-Tools\">Javadoc Tools</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://hackmd.io/_uploads/SyaZOd8Ybe.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"Before\">Before</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://hackmd.io/_uploads/BJ-2a_IF-g.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p>漂浮視窗</p>\n<h3 id=\"After-2\">After</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://hackmd.io/_uploads/SyM9Ou8t-x.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p>點選 Java Class 可以直接 preview Java Doc</p>\n<h1>🔗 參考資料</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/redhat-developer/vscode-java/issues/3773\">Improve readability of javadoc #3773</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/java/java-linting\">Java formatting and linting</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/redhat-developer/vscode-java\">vscode-java</a></li>\n</ul>\n","_path":"/zh-TW/tutorial-vscode-java-intellij-extension/","_link":"https://hsiangjenli.github.io/blog/zh-TW/tutorial-vscode-java-intellij-extension/","_id":"cmnrj7ye6002vt8zf34lb27sp"}}